defaultInsufficient Capacity in Land Management
default – although the 
defaultdirectorates and agencies
default involved in land have good skills within their particular la
defaultnd disciplines, the government is missing resources that have a wider perspective of land administration and management and can understand the wider land policy issues. This just serves to compound the fragmented and un-coordinated management of land in 
defaultSc
defaultotland
default.
